title: NOT!
lyrics:
They say people are born different
But why does it feel like we’re all the same
Us brain washed into the same system
They expect perfection
So how can we be different
It wasn’t until I saw my reflection

That’s when I woke up and realized

That the truth had been hidden away from us

A sign, an omen, a , a GLITCH

Uisimseuleoun i sesang-eun wae naleul honlanseuleobge halkka

Kkeut-eobs-i manh-eun gomindeul-i nae meolis-sog-e meomulleo

Naneun deougdeo gadhyeoissneun neukkim-i deunda

Yeogin eodilkka naega nugulkka nan naega aniya

Nae jasin-eul bomyeo naega naega anida

Laneun geos-eul alge doego

Geu sungan naneun kkaeeonassda

Nan naega aniya

Wae geudong-an jago iss-eossdeon geonde

Nan naega aniya

Ije kkaeeonaseo beos-eonaya hae

I gong-gan-eseo yeogin eodi nae meolis-sog-e temple

Naui jib naleul sog-yeo heuleum kkaeya haneun tempo

Huimihan mueongaleul chaj-abolyeo aeleul sseo

Seoseohi du nun-eul gam-eulsulog seonmyeonghaejineun light uh

Eodum sog-e nae jasin-i boilkka jigeum nun-eul tteo
